headline: South African Travellers to Take More Holidays in 2025 - Marriott Bonvoy ResearchSurveyed South Africans are planning an average of 2.7 domestic holidays, two short-haul holidays (four-hour flight or less), and 1.8 long-haul holidays in 2025
summary: Research among over 2,000 South African travellers reveals that more than six in 10 plan to take more holidays in 2025.	Bravecations and heritage holidays emerge as key travel trends for 2025.	Savvy...
